conversation.text: Hello, this is Samarth, HR Executive from Kainskep Solutions. How are you today?
[happy] That's great to hear. Are you currently looking for opportunities in any domain?
Haan, main full stack development role ke liye dekh rahi hoon.
[happy] That's great. May I know which domain you are currently interested in?
Haan, maine bolana hai full stack development.

Ah, my apologies. You did mention Full Stack Development. [happy] That's a domain we frequently hire for.

Could you please tell me how many years of experience you have in full stack development?
I have five point five years of experience.
[happy] Five and a half years, that's excellent. And are you currently working somewhere?
[happy] Great. Could you please share your current company and your current role with me?
Current company is HP and my current role is software development.

[happy] Thank you. So, you're a Software Developer at HP with five and a half years of experience. That's very clear.

Could you also let me know what your current CTC is and what your expected CTC would be for a new role?
The current CTC is five LPA. My expected CTC is eight LPA.

[happy] Thank you for sharing that. Eight LPA sounds good.

Could you also let me know what your notice period is at your current company?
My current notice period is forty-five days.

[slow] Alright, forty-five days.

And regarding your current location, where are you currently based? And are you open to relocating to Jaipur for this role?
